1 Section 1. The Senate hereby honors Shawnee Chief Nonhelema Hokolesqua as
2 part of Women's History Month.
3 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and memory
4 of Shawnee Chief Nonhelema Hokolesqua.
5 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
6 Resolution to Senator Reginald Thomas for delivery.
